properties.Weather:
SELECT startTime AS start_time,endTime AS end_time, temperature,temperatureUnit AS temperature_unit,
detailedForecast AS detailed_forecast, CURRENT_DATE AS today,
CASE
WHEN Location = 'Hightop' THEN 1
WHEN Location = 'Eagle Rock' THEN 2
END AS location_id
FROM FLOWFILE
properties.LocationID:
SELECT
DISTINCT Location AS name, Coords AS coords,
CASE
WHEN Location = 'Hightop' THEN 1
WHEN Location = 'Eagle Rock' THEN 2
END AS id
FROM FLOWFILE
